lead_paragraph: Peyton Little scored 17 points to lead No. 13 Oklahoma to a 74-60 victory over South Dakota State on Wednesday night.

headline.print_headline: Little Scores 17; No. 13 Oklahoma Women Beat S. Dakota St.
